            "title": "盤中速報 - 台虹(8039)股價殺至跌停，跌停價145.0元，成交27,562張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8039:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8039-TW</a>)23日09:41下跌16元，股價跌停報145.0元，委買1,962張、委賣148張，成交27,562張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為高分子薄膜銅箔積層板。保護膠片。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8039:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8039-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲20.15%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.15%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+2,736 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,732 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-18 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+1,022 張</li> <li>融資增減：+570 張</li> <li>融券增減：+94 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
